OL,3,CVAR calls to be explained on stadium
OL,4,Cscreens and to TV viewers at Euros
OL,6,FVAR decisions will be explained in
OL,7,Fmore detail at Euro 2024 to provide
OL,8,Fgreater clarity to fans and media,
OL,9,FUEFA has announced.
OL,11,FTechnical explanations of off-field
OL,12,Fverdicts will be shown on big screens
OL,13,Finside stadiums and will be given to
OL,14,Fbroadcasters to outline as quickly as
OL,15,Fpossible the rationale behind each
OL,16,Fdecision.
