OL,3,CVAR calls to be explained on stadium
OL,4,Cscreens and to TV viewers at Euros
OL,6,FFor instance, rather than showing that
OL,7,Fa penalty was awarded for a handball,
OL,8,Fthe explanation will detail which
OL,9,Fplayer, which arm, and why that
OL,10,Fplayer's positioning justifies the
OL,11,FVAR's conclusion.
OL,13,FThe shift to a more transparent
OL,14,Fprocess was outlined on Wednesday in
OL,15,FMunich by UEFA managing director for
OL,16,Frefereeing Roberto Rosetti.
