OL,3,CVAR calls to be explained on stadium
OL,4,Cscreens and to TV viewers at Euros
OL,6,FHe said the presentation he gave to
OL,7,Fthe media was also shown to players
OL,8,Fand coaches to ensure everyone was on
OL,9,Fthe same page ahead of the tournament,
OL,10,Fwhich starts on Friday.
OL,12,FAs was previously announced, UEFA is
OL,13,Falso introducing "connected ball
OL,14,Ftechnology" for the first time at a
OL,15,FEuropean Championship, with tech
OL,16,Finside match balls that will send
OL,17,Fprecise data to video match officials
OL,18,Fin real time.
