OL,4,Cscreens and to TV viewers at Euros
OL,6,FThe technology, which also combines
OL,7,Fplayer position data with AI and
OL,8,Fcontributes to UEFA's semi-automated
OL,9,Foffside technology, was used at both
OL,10,Fthe men's World Cup in 2022 and the
OL,11,Fwomen's edition last summer.
OL,13,FOrganisers feel the innovation, which
OL,14,Fcan help VAR officials identify every
OL,15,Findividual touch of the ball, speeds
OL,16,Fup decision-making when it comes to
OL,17,Fresolving handball and penalty
OL,18,Fincidents.
