OL,6,FIt pinpoints the exact moment the ball
OL,7,Fis touched, and therefore can also
OL,8,Fhelp determine if the ball has touched
OL,9,Fa player's arm or hand.
OL,11,FThe public will also be able to see a
OL,12,Fvisual representation of this
OL,13,Ftechnology at work during replays.
